297
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,440
I'm sorry.

298
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,390
So sorry, everyone.

299
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:41,480
Let's go on.

300
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,720
That was just a little incident.

301
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:44,870
Gao Xiang?

302
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:46,750
Who was it?

303
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:51,120
That ungrateful guy, Yang Hui.

304
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,510
Your nephew in the army?

305
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,510
He doesn't look ungrateful.

306
00:11:58,790 --> 00:11:59,720
I told you your letter

307
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,910
was too harsh that day.

308
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,630
All I did

309
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,670
was repeat your words.

310
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:06,360
I didn't know the real situation.

311
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:07,960
Look at him.

312
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,270
You probably misunderstood him.

313
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:13,840
Tops and pants are all available!

314
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:14,870
It makes your legs

315
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,630
look longer and slimmer!

316
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:18,080
You can try them on over there.

317
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:18,870
Here.

318
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:20,550
Anything you like, miss?

319
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,270
Lady, this is men's clothing.

320
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:24,120
Women's is over there.

321
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:25,750
I'm shopping for my boyfriend.

322
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,840
But I can't be sure about the size.

323
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,360
It's fine.

324
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,600
Just find someone to try it on

325
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,270
for you.

326
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,750
What's his height and weight?

327
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,440
About the same as him.

328
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:41,670
Come and help.

329
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:45,840
Thank you.

330
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:47,000
Try it over your uniform.

331
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:47,630
Sorry, this is

332
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,270
a military uniform.

333
00:12:49,550 --> 00:12:50,200
I can't put it on.

334
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:52,910
However...

335
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,360
For this jacket,

336
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:55,870
take one size bigger.

337
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,630
Why should we believe you?

338
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,720
What if it doesn't

339
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,600
fit properly?

340
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,240
Never mind.

341
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:01,670
No,

342
00:13:01,790 --> 00:13:02,270
Auntie,

343
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,080
I mean I can't wear it over my uniform.

344
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,720
But I can go to the fitting room,

345
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,550
take off my uniform,

346
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:07,960
and try it on for you.

347
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,240
Is that okay?

348
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:10,600
That's too much trouble.

349
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,270
Over there.

350
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:19,550
How is it?

351
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,910
It's perfect!

352
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,080
I'll take it.

353
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,510
I'll take it off now.

354
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,120
No need.

355
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,600
I'll get you a new one.

356
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:27,960
You don't need

357
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,080
to keep order anymore.

358
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,030
Just go sell

359
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:31,150
men's clothing in this.

360
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:33,750
Not willing to?

361
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:34,870
Yes, I am.

362
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,550
I never thought I'd be

363
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:37,960
a fashion model for you, Auntie.

364
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,200
It's my pleasure.

365
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,360
Let me get you a new one.

366
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:47,670
How much is it?

367
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,120
Wait.

368
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:48,480
It's 120 yuan.

369
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:49,000
Okay.

370
00:13:58,510 --> 00:13:59,480
Wrap it up for me.

371
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,000
Okay.

372
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:03,390
Thanks.

373
00:14:03,510 --> 00:14:05,000
Thank you, everyone.

374
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,120
Every customer

375
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,440
is a good friend to us.

376
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,630
Now,

377
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:10,840
let's call it a day.

378
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:13,360
If you like me

379
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:15,120
and like our clothes,

380
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:17,080
remember to come back tomorrow!

381
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,030
Love you all!

382
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,080
Thank you!

383
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,630
We'll hold another sales event

384
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:25,510
here tomorrow.

385
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:26,440
You're all welcome

386
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:28,200
to come tomorrow
with friends and relatives.

387
00:14:28,550 --> 00:14:29,440
Come back tomorrow!

388
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:36,360
Yang Hui, right?

389
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:40,240
I'm Hao Qianqian.

390
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:42,080
I saw your photos before.

391
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,960
You looked handsome
in a military uniform.

392
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,670
But I never thought you'd look

393
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,870
even more dashing in this jacket!

394
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:51,200
Ms. Hao, you saw my photos?

395
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:51,790
Of course.

396
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,630
Wanzhi and I are good friends.

397
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,390
So you're like my auntie.

398
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:56,910
Oh, don't say that.

399
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,440
I'm not that much older than you.

400
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,870
Just call me

401
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:00,960
Qian.

402
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,270
Ms. Hao...

403
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,510
Quit flirting.

404
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,480
Time to leave work.

405
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,440
Yang Hui and his friends

406
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,510
really helped us out.

407
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,240
You should treat them
to late‑night snacks.

408
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:13,840
It's on me.

409
00:15:20,910 --> 00:15:21,480
Auntie,

410
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:22,910
I sold

411
00:15:22,910 --> 00:15:23,790
twelve pairs of jeans

412
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:24,910
and nine denim jackets,

413
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,080
mostly at a 10% discount.

414
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,080
One lady kept haggling,

415
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,720
and since she bought three pieces,

416
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:30,910
I cut her 40 yuan off the total.

417
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:33,790
The total revenue is 1,235 yuan.

418
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,630
It's all here.

419
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,030
You remembered it so clearly?

420
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,200
Quite impressive.

421
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,030
My name is Li Juan,

422
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,360
your auntie's best friend.

423
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,240
Hello,

424
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,150
I'm Yang Hui.

425
00:15:45,390 --> 00:15:45,870
I know.

426
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:47,270
Juan,

427
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:48,240
check the numbers.

428
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,390
See if his numbers are right.

429
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,630
How could it be wrong?

430
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:52,600
Here.

431
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:53,670
You two chat.

432
00:15:58,720 --> 00:15:59,750
How did you find me here?

433
00:16:00,630 --> 00:16:02,030
I followed the stamp on the letter.

434
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,670
And I asked around

435
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,080
and found the house you rented.

436
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,360
Then I asked the landlord

437
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,720
and came to Dongmen Market.

438
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:08,840
Not bad.

439
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,840
You even learned
to spy on me in the army?

440
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,150
I dare not.

441
00:16:16,270 --> 00:16:17,600
Why didn't you write me back?

442
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,200
I didn't dare.

443
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,000
I scolded you in the letter.

444
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,120
Don't you have

445
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:23,960
any explanation?

446
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:27,200
I dare not.

447
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,790
I don't want to hear that.

448
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,030
I really didn't dare, Auntie.

449
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:30,960
You scolded me.

450
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:31,960
That means you were angry.

451
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,870
How could I dare explain?

452
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:38,120
Your unit must

453
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,030
be pretty strict.

454
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:40,670
Why come to Shenzhen?

455
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,440
The training is over.

456
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,600
I have a few days off.

457
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,480
So I talked it over with my comrades

458
00:16:45,670 --> 00:16:46,360
and came here.

459
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,270
Wanna borrow money?

460
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,440
Let me tell you, I don't have any.

461
00:16:51,390 --> 00:16:52,150
But you made

462
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:53,120
quite a lot of money today.

463
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:56,360
You think I got the clothes for free?

464
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,960
And I have to pay the stall rent.

465
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,670
Well, you did help me today.

466
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,510
Can't let you work for free.

467
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:06,440
Here.

468
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,680
Treat your friends.

469
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:10,030
Want more?

470
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,240
Let me tell you,

471
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,350
that's all you can get

472
00:17:12,350 --> 00:17:13,590
from me, not a penny more.

473
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:14,440
No, Auntie.

474
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:15,550
You misunderstood.

475
00:17:16,070 --> 00:17:16,790
I didn't come

476
00:17:16,790 --> 00:17:17,790
to borrow money.

477
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,030
I don't need money anymore.

478
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,510
It's already passed.

479
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,640
What has passed?

480
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,070
Let me explain.

481
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,790
A few months ago,

482
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:28,640
my comrade who enlisted with me

483
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,590
was badly injured during training

484
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,350
and may be disabled for life.

485
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,110
Though the army would help,

486
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,240
the rest of us

487
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:35,880
still wanted

488
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:36,920
to raise money

489
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:37,960
for his family.

490
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:39,720
But I didn't

491
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,830
have that much money.

492
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:43,030
So I could only write to you.

493
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,400
You idiot...

494
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,350
Why didn't you write

495
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:49,110
such an important thing in the letter?

496
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,640
It was my own problem.

497
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,160
It had nothing to do with you, so...

498
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,070
Then...

499
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,000
But if your comrades

500
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,200
contributed money and you didn't,

501
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,830
they'd look down on you.

502
00:17:58,310 --> 00:17:58,880
I did.

503
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:00,510
How come you have money?

504
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,510
I borrowed two years'
allowance in advance.

505
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,030
You could do that?

506
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:06,440
Your unit has such a policy?

507
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,830
No, my commander lent it to me.

508
00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:10,240
I'll pay him back monthly.

509
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,510
I'll pay it for you.

510
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,480
You can't owe him.

511
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:17,790
No, Auntie.

512
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,110
This is an agreement

513
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:19,830
between soldiers.

514
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:20,440
Can't be changed.

515
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:22,000
Also, you...

516
00:18:23,550 --> 00:18:24,960
You're having a tough time.

517
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,200
Having a tough time?

518
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,270
I'm running a big business here.

519
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:36,070
Do you know how much

520
00:18:36,070 --> 00:18:36,920
our revenue is today?

521
00:18:39,270 --> 00:18:39,960
Auntie,

522
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:42,830
your capital is borrowed.

523
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:45,590
You bought too many goods,
but they haven't sold well.

524
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:47,640
That's why you arranged this event,

525
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,160
am I right?

526
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,200
Actually, I arrived this noon.

527
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:52,000
And I checked

528
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:53,550
the street markets

529
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:54,550
around this block.

530
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,160
When I found this street

531
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,550
and saw you,

532
00:18:59,070 --> 00:18:59,920
I understood right away.

533
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,590
If you had enough money,

534
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,790
you wouldn't rent a stall here.

535
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,350
After all, this street
is the quietest one.

536
00:19:06,830 --> 00:19:08,830
So the rent here is cheap.

537
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,350
I also talked to a few

538
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,030
stall owners here.

539
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:13,720
They said your business has

540
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:15,200
been bad these past few months.

541
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:18,640
So you ordered this batch of goods

542
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:22,310
as a desperate gamble, right?

543
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,200
And you said you didn't spy on me?

544
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:28,880
I...

545
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:29,960
I'm sorry, Auntie.

546
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,000
I wasn't spying on anyone.

547
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,640
I just happened to hear them.

548
00:19:39,830 --> 00:19:40,550
It's quite late.

549
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:42,000
I'll skip the late‑night snacks.

550
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:42,920
Please help me

551
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,240
explain this to Ms. Hao later.

552
00:19:50,270 --> 00:19:50,720
Oh, right.

553
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:53,070
I... I see you have
quite a lot of goods there.

554
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,110
I don't think you need

555
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:54,920
to move them.

556
00:19:55,270 --> 00:19:56,440
It will be too much trouble.

557
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,200
We'll keep

558
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:58,960
an eye on things for you tonight.

559
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,200
I see you've got cots.

560
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,510
We can take turns sleeping.

561
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:04,750
Okay.

562
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:06,920
There are tarps there.

563
00:20:07,030 --> 00:20:07,880
If it rains,

564
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:09,110
cover the clothes.

565
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:10,680
If the clothes get wet,

566
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:11,920
you'll pay for them.

567
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:17,480
Don't worry, Auntie.

568
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:30,030
Qian,

569
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:30,960
you take the bed.

570
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,000
You treat me the best.

571
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:34,880
But these noodles

572
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:36,350
taste so awful.

573
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:40,200
If Yang Hui were here right now,

574
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,270
I could eat them.

575
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:42,790
Just drink your water.

576
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,790
What?

577
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,510
Your nephew is really nice.

578
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:50,790
You should have

579
00:20:50,790 --> 00:20:52,590
set us up back then.

580
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:53,510
Kick her!

581
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:54,880
If it weren't

582
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,920
for her singing,

583
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,000
I'd have kicked her already.

584
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,960
Quit joking around now.

585
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:00,200
Joking like that?

586
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:01,270
Don't you think of Zhu?

587
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,960
And who'd think of me?

588
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:07,590
Hey, we forgot Mr. Gao!

589
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:08,160
We haven't even

590
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,720
treated him to a meal or something!

591
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,110
Why are you so excited?

592
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:14,400
Wanzhi is the one he likes.

593
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:15,480
Why do you care?

594
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:16,350
He will

595
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,960
definitely come to help tomorrow.

596
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,400
Don't talk nonsense.

597
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:21,350
He's just afraid I won't pay him back

598
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:22,160
and will run away.

599
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:26,400
We didn't sell enough today.

600
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,310
We must keep it up tomorrow.

601
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,240
Qian,

602
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:32,790
can you sing all day?

603
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,480
If it's to Yang Hui,

604
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:37,310
I can.

605
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:39,310
You need a beating.

606
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,270
The three of us

607
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:53,440
are finally together again.

608
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:54,680
So nice.

609
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,880
What I miss most

610
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:58,480
is that shipping container

611
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,750
on the construction site.

612
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:01,960
But this house is better.

613
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:02,790
It's bigger.

614
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:04,200
It's a promise, right?

615
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:06,070
Once we make some money,

616
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:07,160
you have to put

617
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:08,110
another bed here for me,

618
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,000
with a big

619
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:10,960
and soft mattress on top.

620
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,240
Okay.

621
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:13,920
Don't you love to dream?

622
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:15,440
Close your eyes,

623
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,960
and the mattress is there.

624
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,960
Shenzhen is so nice.

625
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:50,640
♪Sweet as honey,♪

626
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:55,030
♪your smile is sweet as honey.♪

627
00:22:55,030 --> 00:23:00,680
♪Like flowers blooming
in the spring breeze.♪

628
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:05,720
♪Blooming in the spring breeze.♪

629
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:10,830
♪Where, oh where,♪

630
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:14,720
♪have I seen you before?♪

631
00:23:15,310 --> 00:23:16,200
This is the latest style!

632
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:17,880
They are on the models.

633
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,720
You can try them on if you like.

634
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:20,350
Take a look!

635
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,350
Thank you for your purchase!

636
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:25,400
Okay, thank you, lady.

637
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:28,550
If you see anything
you like, just try it on.

638
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:29,750
You can try them on over there.

639
00:23:29,830 --> 00:23:30,830
There's a fitting room.

640
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:34,480
This is 85 yuan.

641
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,640
It's a little too big for you.

642
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,270
You can try it on
in the fitting room there.

643
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,200
The cut on this one is great, girl!

644
00:23:39,310 --> 00:23:40,200
This one is 130 yuan.

645
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,030
Look at this one.

646
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:43,350
It will look great on you.

647
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:44,830
Small size...

648
00:23:44,830 --> 00:23:45,750
I'll get you another one.

649
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:46,830
A moment, please.

650
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:47,920
Yes, this one will do.

651
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:49,550
Try it on in the fitting room.

652
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:53,350
Try them on if you like.

653
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,440
Nice products.

654
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:02,790
Where did you get them?

655
00:24:03,830 --> 00:24:04,440
Sorry.

656
00:24:04,590 --> 00:24:05,590
Commercial secret.

657
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,680
Such good quality.

658
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:12,720
If you rented my stall,

659
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:14,110
they'd sell out within a few days.

660
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:16,000
I can't afford the rent.

661
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:18,920
Just ask me again.

662
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,160
I'm in a good mood.

663
00:24:20,550 --> 00:24:22,000
Maybe I can give you a 30% discount.

664
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:23,550
But I'm in a bad mood.

665
00:24:23,550 --> 00:24:24,480
I don't feel like asking.

666
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,160
Strong personality.

667
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,550
I've never seen anyone

668
00:24:31,550 --> 00:24:32,110
as fierce as you

669
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:33,000
in Dongmen Market.

670
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:34,750
Selling such good products

671
00:24:34,750 --> 00:24:36,000
in such a remote spot,

672
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,720
even hiring a singer to promote them...

673
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:39,350
Do you really think

674
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:41,110
you can turn the market upside down?

675
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,830
Why would I?

676
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,200
If I turned this place upside down,

677
00:24:46,350 --> 00:24:47,680
how could I do business then?

678
00:24:48,550 --> 00:24:49,440
Are you buying clothes?

679
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:50,510
If not, move.

680
00:24:51,310 --> 00:24:51,960
Miss!

681
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:53,590
Are you shopping

682
00:24:53,590 --> 00:24:54,960
for yourself or for a friend?

683
00:25:03,790 --> 00:25:05,000
I really need to say it.

684
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:07,550
He came all the way
to Shenzhen to see you,

685
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:09,070
and he helped you so much,

686
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:11,000
but you didn't even treat him to a meal.

687
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:12,070
He volunteered.

688
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,240
He just came at a bad time.

689
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:15,350
I don't have time for that.

690
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:16,440
He's been

691
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,200
sleeping on the street every day.

692
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:19,310
You are

693
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:20,270
quite an aunt.

694
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,960
I have no choice.

695
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,310
It's already so busy now.

696
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,270
If we had more goods,

697
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:25,720
we'd all be exhausted.

698
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,240
Well, he's my nephew, anyway.

699
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,240
Helping me is his duty.

700
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,240
Why are you laughing?

701
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:34,440
I'm his auntie.

702
00:25:34,510 --> 00:25:35,720
Shouldn't he help me?

703
00:25:36,550 --> 00:25:37,310
Done counting?

704
00:25:37,750 --> 00:25:38,440
Done.

705
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:40,070
Sales are better than yesterday,

706
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,400
but we're still far

707
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,160
from covering the cost of the goods.

708
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:45,440
We only have three days.

709
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:46,830
Wanzhi,

710
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,240
do you have any other ideas?

711
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,000
To be honest,

712
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,350
you two should have

713
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,000
told me earlier

714
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,880
you were doing such big business.

715
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,640
If you had,

716
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,680
I'd have borrowed some from Liu.

717
00:26:00,550 --> 00:26:01,790
There's no time.

718
00:26:01,830 --> 00:26:02,880
I've already crossed him.

719
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,920
Asking him for money now?

720
00:26:04,070 --> 00:26:05,200
No way.

721
00:26:07,790 --> 00:26:09,480
I shouldn't be using your money anyway.

722
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:10,960
Wanzhi,

723
00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:12,830
if we ask Mr. Gao

724
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:13,480
for help again,

725
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:14,510
will he give us a hand?

726
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,960
Of course.

727
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:18,000
As long as Wanzhi asks him...

728
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:20,920
No way.

729
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,350
You don't know men.

730
00:26:24,110 --> 00:26:25,270
The more you need him,

731
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:26,440
the happier he gets.

732
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:27,920
Just try it. You'll see.

733
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:40,200
Hui?

734
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,030
Hui,

735
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:43,590
can you get me a bottle of water?

736
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:44,830
Alright.

737
00:26:45,790 --> 00:26:46,270
Here you go.

738
00:26:47,550 --> 00:26:48,920
My arms are tired.

739
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:50,160
Help me open it.

740
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:50,920
Okay.

741
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,030
You see, both my hands

742
00:26:55,030 --> 00:26:56,200
are occupied.

743
00:26:56,960 --> 00:26:58,030
Could you feed me?

744
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:00,350
Just a second.

745
00:27:09,750 --> 00:27:10,720
Here, have some herbal tea.

746
00:27:11,070 --> 00:27:12,400
It's good for your throat.

747
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:14,270
You're already

748
00:27:14,270 --> 00:27:15,750
so considerate at such a young age!

749
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,270
You've worked the hardest.

750
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,920
Even those big stars

751
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:20,590
don't sing

752
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,030
as long as you do.

753
00:27:22,750 --> 00:27:23,880
I thank you on my auntie's behalf.

754
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,750
Fang Wanzhi, busy, huh?

755
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,160
You know what?

756
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:51,960
Your idea

757
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:53,070
is quite impressive.

758
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,070
When I go

759
00:27:54,070 --> 00:27:55,110
back to school,

760
00:27:55,110 --> 00:27:56,680
I can share this as a success story

761
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,830
with the students.

762
00:27:58,720 --> 00:28:00,310
I've made a preliminary
estimate for you.

763
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:02,160
The traffic from your promotion

764
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:03,790
can boost revenue

765
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:05,160
seven to ten times.

766
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:07,240
Mr. Gao,

767
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:09,720
I need to discuss something with you.

768
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:11,640
Perfect timing.

769
00:28:12,110 --> 00:28:12,960
I also have something

770
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:13,880
to discuss with you.

771
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:14,550
You go first.

772
00:28:14,750 --> 00:28:15,480
You go.

773
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,030
Well, here's the thing.

774
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,880
That 130,000 yuan

775
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:20,640
was borrowed from

776
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,750
four different classmates.

777
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:23,310
One of them lent us 30,000.

778
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,030
He called this morning,

779
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:26,830
saying he urgently needed the money

780
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:28,000
and hoped we could repay him

781
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:28,880
as soon as possible.

782
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,790
He said he'd waive the interest.

783
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:32,550
You see...

784
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:36,750
Okay.

785
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,030
I'll pay him back

786
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:39,200
as soon as I recover the costs.

787
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,310
Okay. That's all.

788
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:42,240
Your turn.

789
00:28:43,830 --> 00:28:44,960
It's nothing.

790
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:46,880
Hey, just say it. It's fine.

791
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:47,960
No. No.

792
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:50,000
I just forgot.

793
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:52,400
Couldn't recall it.

794
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:53,790
Let me think...

795
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:56,110
Oh, your memory...

796
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:16,720
Wanzhi?

797
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:19,550
Thanks.

798
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,400
Wanzhi,

799
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:22,110
you're amazing!

800
00:29:22,510 --> 00:29:24,400
Business has improved
across the entire street!

801
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,550
Everyone is praising you.

802
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,590
I can sell dozens

803
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:28,510
more kilos

804
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:29,480
of tea a day!

805
00:29:31,790 --> 00:29:32,480
Glad to hear that.

806
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:34,200
But why

807
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,310
are you sitting here,

808
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:36,590
looking all gloomy?

809
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:41,550
Business is good, indeed.

810
00:29:42,030 --> 00:29:42,680
However,

811
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:44,590
the returns are still too slow.

812
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:47,160
Our customers are all individuals.

813
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:48,510
So of course it's slow.

814
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,110
Mr. Gold Tooth's clients

815
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:52,160
are all wholesalers.

816
00:29:52,510 --> 00:29:54,160
If this batch of goods were his,

817
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:55,160
it'd be gone in minutes.

818
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,400
You know Mr. Gold Tooth, too?

819
00:29:58,510 --> 00:30:00,270
Everyone in Dongmen Market knows him.

820
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:01,920
He came to me yesterday,

821
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,030
asking where you got

822
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:03,830
these goods from.

823
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:04,830
I didn't know.

824
00:30:05,510 --> 00:30:06,030
Even if I did,

825
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:07,070
I wouldn't tell him.

826
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:08,400
That's business rules.

827
00:30:10,310 --> 00:30:10,880
Miss?

828
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,070
How much is this tea?

829
00:30:14,030 --> 00:30:14,640
Which one?

830
00:30:17,070 --> 00:30:17,510
Here.

831
00:30:24,590 --> 00:30:25,200
Sir!

832
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:26,640
Sourcing goods?

833
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,240
Yes.

834
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:27,920
Where do you sell?

835
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:29,030
Chengdu or Wuhan?

836
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:29,880
Well, I...

837
00:30:30,270 --> 00:30:32,000
I have a batch of top-quality goods.

838
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:32,880
Want to take a look?

839
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:35,310
I've bought enough goods this time.

840
00:30:35,310 --> 00:30:35,920
I'm sorry.

841
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:38,070
But you can give me your phone number.

842
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:39,350
I'll come straight to you

843
00:30:39,350 --> 00:30:40,030
next time I'm here.

844
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:40,680
Is that okay?

845
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:41,920
Yes.

846
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:43,640
This is my pager number.

847
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,680
Page me when you come again.

848
00:30:45,790 --> 00:30:46,480
Alright, girl.

849
00:30:46,590 --> 00:30:47,350
I'll head off now.

850
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:48,310
I'll treat you next time,

851
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:48,750
okay?

852
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:49,070
Alright.

853
00:30:49,350 --> 00:30:49,920
Sir, are you

854
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:50,960
sourcing goods?

855
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:51,750
Mr. Chen! Move on!

856
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:52,880
Mr. Chen! Keep going!

857
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,440
Hey, girl,

858
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:58,590
you're in my territory,

859
00:30:58,590 --> 00:30:59,830
stealing my customers?

860
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,480
That's ridiculous.

861
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,240
Mr. Gold Tooth,

862
00:31:03,550 --> 00:31:05,270
your business has grown so big.

863
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:06,720
All these stores are yours, right?

864
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:07,750
One or two customers

865
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:10,070
don't mean much to you, right?

866
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:12,030
You're breaking the rules.

867
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,880
I don't have any other choice.

868
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:15,000
Didn't you also ask

869
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,200
about my supply channels?

870
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:16,880
I...

871
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:19,270
My clothes were indeed pretty good.

872
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:20,960
I was planning to sell them slowly.

873
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:21,680
However,

874
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:23,310
if you find out my channels,

875
00:31:23,310 --> 00:31:24,480
I won't be able to sell them.

876
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:26,350
So I have no choice but to act first.

877
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,200
Oh, miss!

878
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:29,000
Why are you so bold?

879
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:29,960
Who's your boss?

880
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,200
I'm the boss.

881
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,240
Don't forget about our bet.

882
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:36,640
As things stand, you definitely

883
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,960
won't lose by year's end.

884
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,110
I'm a man of my word.

885
