00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,590
Ms. Fang, you are

1174
00:40:59,670 --> 00:41:00,280
very decisive.

1175
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,110
You flatter me.

1176
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:03,800
It's all thanks to you, Mr. Huang.

1177
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:07,670
How did I not notice

1178
00:41:08,190 --> 00:41:09,960
such a beautiful and outstanding woman

1179
00:41:10,230 --> 00:41:11,550
working in my factory?

1180
00:41:12,510 --> 00:41:13,360
Nan is nothing

1181
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:15,440
compared to you.

1182
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:17,510
Mr. Huang, saying that

1183
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,510
isn't very respectful.

1184
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,360
Don't get me wrong.

1185
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:22,030
What I mean is

1186
00:41:22,590 --> 00:41:23,670
Nan simply

1187
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,280
isn't in your league.

1188
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:27,030
Alright, cut the chitchat.

1189
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,400
Just get the accountant here.

1190
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:29,710
The truck is here in 10 minutes.

1191
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,760
Fine, I'll arrange it.

1192
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,440
Make sure to secure the goods!

1193
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:34,960
Alright.

1194
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,230
Are all the goods here?

1195
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:36,880
Yes.

1196
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:37,670
They are.

1197
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:38,190
Okay.

1198
00:41:40,630 --> 00:41:41,400
Here, let me help you.

1199
00:41:42,630 --> 00:41:43,840
Maybe we can have dinner

1200
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,190
together sometime.

1201
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:47,400
Our factory's products

1202
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,360
are of high quality.

1203
00:41:49,110 --> 00:41:50,150
I'd be glad

1204
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:51,840
to continue our cooperation.

1205
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:54,480
If this batch sells well,

1206
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,190
we can continue production.

1207
00:41:56,590 --> 00:41:57,800
We can have dinner sometime.

1208
00:41:58,280 --> 00:41:59,800
But I'll need to schedule it first.

1209
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:02,320
Oh... Of course.

1210
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:03,840
Just give me a call

1211
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:04,510
if you have time.

1212
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:05,840
No problem.

1213
00:42:16,670 --> 00:42:17,280
Ms. Fang,

1214
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,880
this is our delivery slip.

1215
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,280
You'll need it to pick up the goods.

1216
00:42:22,110 --> 00:42:22,960
What did you just call me?

1217
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:24,590
Ms. Fang.

1218
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:27,360
I'm not quite used to that.

1219
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,510
You're so young

1220
00:42:29,550 --> 00:42:30,480
and so pretty.

1221
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,510
If I were more superficial,

1222
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:33,480
I'd just call you pretty.

1223
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,880
But with such a big business,

1224
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:37,510
I wouldn't dare.

1225
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:38,880
If I offend you, Ms. Fang,

1226
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,150
my boss will surely fire me.

1227
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:42,230
How will you get back?

1228
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:43,440
Let me hail a cab for you.

1229
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:44,320
Okay.

1230
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,400
Just a minute.

1231
00:42:53,510 --> 00:42:54,630
Thanks, Ms. Fang.
